        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/herohtar/{size}/43780_2.png",
        "created_at": "2024-12-28T06:57:06.740Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal uses phone numbers as the sole identifier for your account. If you become unregistered and no longer have access to the phone number, you will not be able to register again with that number.</p>\n<p>There is an existing feature request about registering using other means:</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"2222\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/l/22d042/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/registration-without-a-phone-number/2222\">Registration without a phone number</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Iâ€™m quite sure that there are issues similar to this one. \nI would like to have the possibility to register to Signal without a phone number but maybe with an email or just an user name . I have got really young cousins that have got phones just to play games and sending whatsapp messages and they have to pay 15 euros or more to have a SIM card. Itâ€™s unbelivableâ€¦ i think that it could be done without problem\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
